    "description": "随着丹德里恩的吟游歌谣，扮演杰洛特踏上冒险之旅。《Reigns: The Witcher》是 Nerial 与 Devolver Digital 联手打造、广受好评的《Reigns》系列最新“突变”之作。以 CD PROJEKT RED 备受赞誉的《巫师》系列为背景，在残酷而神秘的黑暗奇幻世界中缓缓展开。<br><br>化身利维亚的杰洛特——传奇猎魔人，探索抉择与后果交织的世界，在吟游诗人的醉人歌谣中为生存而战。你会勇往直前猎杀怪物吗？还是桀骜不驯，即使得罪当地人也毫不在意？又或是只想简单泡个热水澡？开启这段旅程，谱写你的史诗，有朝一日赢得不朽之名。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1651600/extras/448261531239c0721b55a8688e43c8e7.poster.avif?t=1772038304\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1651600/extras/448261531239c0721b55a8688e43c8e7.webm?t=1772038304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1651600/extras/448261531239c0721b55a8688e43c8e7.mp4?t=1772038304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >猎魔人的使命永无止境</h2>世间形形色色的人会找你完成各种委托，有的危机四伏，有的有损人格，往往需要深入探寻其中的内情。<br>你可以借助丹德里恩的歌谣，体验成千上万种故事情节组合，探索各种戏剧化与奇趣情节的可能。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1651600/extras/5440a9da24cc542d033a5acf4e622323.poster.avif?t=1772038304\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1651600/extras/5440a9da24cc542d033a5acf4e622323.webm?t=1772038304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1651600/extras/5440a9da24cc542d033a5acf4e622323.mp4?t=1772038304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >老友重聚</h2>叶奈法、特莉丝和维瑟米尔等熟悉的面孔会陪伴你度过由吟游诗人复述的难忘冒险。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1651600/extras/f8874fd00c03e2d78c14a1ea582ee189.poster.avif?t=1772038304\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1651600/extras/f8874fd00c03e2d78c14a1ea582ee189.webm?t=1772038304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1651600/extras/f8874fd00c03e2d78c14a1ea582ee189.mp4?t=1772038304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >巡回民谣诗人</h2>踏出酒馆，演绎杰洛特的精彩传奇，解开谜题，解锁新的任务和角色。<br>提升吟游诗人的等级，打造更多史诗叙事，最终登上传奇巅峰。<br><br><i>由 Nerial Limited 开发，CD PROJEKT RED 参与合作</i>",
